        <p>For given level of confidence <italic>q</italic>, 0≤<italic>q</italic>≤1 we can calculate a required read coverage <italic>c</italic> for proper repetitive motif reconstruction, using the Eq. <xref rid="Equ5" ref-type="">5</xref>, where <inline-formula id="IEq6"><alternatives><tex-math id="M19">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
